{"tid":1107851,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"今日番學見到有個女同學唔夠力搬箱重野上樓梯","createTime":"2019-04-15T14:12:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T19:28:41.000Z","uid":218575,"like":1157,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"27625bd7b96b0a4c2dca13246a44f5e7307d634d","tid":1107851,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T14:12:58.000Z","msg":"我諗住係時候展示下男子氣概<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：呢啲粗重野等我黎啦 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：肥仔 唔該曬你呀！！！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：洗乜客氣<br />\n<br />\n烏低身諗住搬起箱野個時<br />\n原來真係幾重下 諗住豆一豆箱野起身<br />\n發力個時唔小心放左個響屁<br />\n嗶！一聲 <br />\n個女同學同附近嘅人笑到仆街<br />\n我硬住頭皮幫佢搬咗上去就急急腳走人了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"746d829396621df655d7b1e1becaac9416df0b09","tid":1107851,"uid":431,"like":60,"dislike":7,"score":53,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T14:14:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://beta-static.photobucket.com/images/ah233/sorsawsor/3/35234e1b-622a-4b20-964f-c69579770dcc-original.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbeta-static.photobucket.com%2Fimages%2Fah233%2Fsorsawsor%2F3%2F35234e1b-622a-4b20-964f-c69579770dcc-original.gif&h=dd661daf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e384a09ac18d483898822447feeb1d39df8eec7","tid":1107851,"uid":218575,"like":260,"dislike":2,"score":258,"quote":{"pid":"746d829396621df655d7b1e1becaac9416df0b09","tid":1107851,"uid":431,"like":60,"dislike":7,"score":53,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T14:14:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://beta-static.photobucket.com/images/ah233/sorsawsor/3/35234e1b-622a-4b20-964f-c69579770dcc-original.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbeta-static.photobucket.com%2Fimages%2Fah233%2Fsorsawsor%2F3%2F35234e1b-622a-4b20-964f-c69579770dcc-original.gif&h=dd661daf&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T14:14:45.000Z","msg":"做乜當con